    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Layers of colored plaster in a casting mold that indicate the proximity of the cast surface; to prevent damage to the cast surface as the mold is chipped away from the cast.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
